bugs, notifications, suggestions and other interactions with the
development team.  Between 11 March 2007
and 18 March 2007, activity on the site has resulted in:
</p>

<ul>
<li>619 new bugs during this period</li>
<li>443 bugs closed or resolved during this period</li>
<li>27 previously closed bugs were reopened this period</li>
<li>152 closed as NEEDINFO/WONTFIX/CANTFIX/INVALID/UPSTREAM during this period</li>
<li>116 bugs marked as duplicates during this period</li>
</ul>

<p>
Of the 10239 currently open bugs: 17 are labeled 'blocker', 107 are labeled
'critical', and 412 are labeled 'major'.
</p>

